title: Healthy Back to School Routines

description:

Time for some preaching! In today's broadcast I talk about three key things to getting back to school and back to healthy routines. You gotta ditch stinking thinking like "It's going to be so hard," make a plan that has all the carpooling, all the meetings, the increased traffic and more included, AND learn to give yourself short windows of time to get your stuff done!
